do is crush Pierce's faith

15:00.324 --> 15:01.938
To feel better about dying.

15:01.939 --> 15:02.866
And...

15:02.928 --> 15:04.886
and now that I realize
that that was my goal...

15:04.887 --> 15:05.756
mm-hmm?

15:06.263 --> 15:08.567
I can really roll up my sleeves

15:08.568 --> 15:09.530
