Will be lying on a
stainless steel slab

15:48.080 --> 15:49.233
For all to see.

15:49.234 --> 15:51.804
Surprise! Welcome to reality.

15:51.805 --> 15:53.048
Welcome to death.

15:53.077 --> 15:54.482
- have fun.
- Good luck.

15:54.925 --> 15:55.904
Wow.

15:56.181 --> 15:57.760
