I'm gone, Pierce.

17:21.284 --> 17:23.057
Gone forever and...

17:23.810 --> 17:25.679
That's how I like it.

17:26.819 --> 17:30.781
Life is only worth a
damn because it's short.

17:31.225 --> 17:34.685
It's designed to
be consumed, used,

17:34.686 --> 17:38.146
spent, lived, felt.

17:38.147 --> 17:40.658
We're supposed to fill
it with every mistake

17:40.659 --> 17:43.244
And miracle we can manage.

17:43.590 --> 17:46.489
And then we're supposed to let go.

17:46.759 --> 17:50.730
I can't force you to do
that for yourself, Pierce.

17:51.077 --> 17:54.364
But you can't force me to stay.

17:54.653 --> 17:58.096
And if you unscrew the
top of that stupid thing,

17:58.097 --> 18:00.628
